

1) mvn archetype:generate -DarchetypeGroupId=org.codehaus.mojo -DarchetypeArtifactId=gwt-maven-plugin -DarchetypeVersion=1.2 -DgroupId=com.mysite.gwtspringmvc -DartifactId=gwt-springmvc-int

2) Edit pom.xml:
2-1) Modify gwt.version in pom.xml to 2.0.4
2-2) Setup web.xml location ([optional] setup copying source WEB-INF as well)
2-3) [optional] setup jetty server configuration - to enable jetty:run-war command
2-4) [optional] setup additional clean step - to delete war directory

3) Edit web.xml, add {spring}-context.xml files

4) Add spring controller

5) Add appropriate mapping as well as other spring config

